# Browsers + profiles offered by the picker.
# Format:  Label|||command      (command may contain quotes; the URL is appended)
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Tip: open the "Browser Picker Rules" app and click "⟳ Rescan profiles" to
# auto-detect every installed browser and profile instead of editing by hand.
Chromium — Default|||chromium --profile-directory=Default
Firefox — default|||firefox -P "default"
